{"tid":1742811,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"（轉貼）cut無國界醫生捐款","createTime":"2019-11-21T02:50:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-23T12:40:45.000Z","uid":49128,"like":30,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"1a9235c517b0168bfd71a3fae6f58c098510f164","tid":1742811,"uid":49128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T02:50:54.000Z","msg":"無國界醫生熱線已廢，想cut捐款但又打唔通hotline，可以直接打去銀行或者網上銀行自己cut，我以HSBC為例，做法係：<br />\n<br />\n1. 先登入HSBC網上理財（一定要電腦版，電話app不能）<br />\n2. 然後喺 &quot;我的銀行&quot; 欄目下揀 &quot;自動轉賬 &quot;<br />\n3. 揀 &quot;管理自動轉賬&quot;，然後就會見到你每月要轉賬嘅項目<br />\n4. 揀返 &quot;Medecins Sans F HK L&quot;，然後 &quot;刪除指示&quot; 再確認<br />\n<br />\n咁就可以成功cut捐款，但我唔知其他銀行網上理財係咪一樣，大家即管試吓！<br />\n<br />\n唔捐都唔夠，要攞返之前捐過嘅錢！方法如下：<br />\n可以打上card centre要求charge back返晒之前所有捐款<br />\nchargeback除咗攞返錢，商戶係要食好貴手續費<br />\n(chargeback 只限 credit card）"},{"pid":"5baa37dba31768745b26e3dbe82278273f70ede1","tid":1742811,"uid":24853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T03:07:27.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8894ed4335ae155f8d8ce9f4e5dd40b20224d263","tid":1742811,"uid":24853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T03:07:45.000Z","msg":"大家快cut"},{"pid":"c8569e36e71fd3f594faa691f9e134ca611c5746","tid":1742811,"uid":70439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T03:12:00.000Z","msg":"要推"},{"pid":"888bd5440a1ee3d05a6174c5f6666f59fd547560","tid":1742811,"uid":47223,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T03:21:06.000Z","msg":"平時就叫香港人可憐下其他地方既人<br />\n香港人有需要既時候就潛水<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e19d5f24b52dbd62c91d97636f0f2965bbb5ed90","tid":1742811,"uid":110653,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T04:36:16.000Z","msg":"唔捐都唔夠，要攞返之前捐過嘅錢！方